<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4272387>
    dc:description "Fig. 30. Head appendages of Helochares (Helochares) pallens (MacLeay, 1825), first instar. A – antenna, dorsal view; B–C – mandibles, dorsal view; D – maxilla, dorsal view; E – maxilla, ventral view; F – labium, dorsal view; G – labium, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4272387/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4272375>
    dc:description "Fig. 24. Enochrus (Methydrus) japonicus (Sharp, 1873), second instar.A – clypeolabrum, dorsal view; B – antenna, dorsal view; C–D – mandibles, dorsal view; E – maxilla, dorsal view; F – maxilla, ventral view; G – labium, dorsal view; H – labium, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4272375/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4272348>
    dc:description "Fig. 12. Agraphydrus narusei (Satô, 1960).A–B – prolegs, ventral view:A – first instar; B – third instar. C–D – shape of setae, dorsal view: C – median part of parietale, third instar, dorsal view; D – thoracic segments, first instar, dorsal view. Seta on PA8 and PA13 missing. Photographs were taken with compound light microscope." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4272348/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4272338>
    dc:description "Fig. 7. Head capsule of Agraphydrus narusei (Satô, 1960), first instar. A – dorsal view; B – ventral view; C – detail of anterior margin of head capsule, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4272338/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4272344>
    dc:description "Fig. 10. Head capsule of Agraphydrus narusei (Satô, 1960), third instar.A – dorsal view; B – ventral view; C – detail of anterior margin of head capsule, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4272344/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4272342>
    dc:description "Fig. 9. Agraphydrus narusei (Satô, 1960), third instar.A – head, dorsal view; B – spiracular atrium, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4272342/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

